item.title: Paradise on Fire
item.description: “The deepest lessons come out of the deepest waters and the hottest fires.” ~ Elisabeth Elliot CA wildfire, Orange skies in SF Bay area, and Dune trailer # It seemed like a weird coincidence that Dune1 trailer2 got released on the same day that the skies in San Francisco turned orange3.
